10 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
11 An Act relating to the State Capitol Preservation
Commission; authorizing the placement of a monument
12 near the State Capitol Arch; directing the State
Capitol Commission to work with private entities to
13 erect the monument; providing for codification; and
declaring an emergency.
14
15
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 4110.2 of Title 74, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 The State Capitol Preservation Commission or designee is hereby
22 authorized to permit and arrange for the placement of the Gold Star
23 Family Monument. This monument shall be designed, constructed, and
24 placed on the Capitol Grounds by private entities at no expense to
HB4486 HFLR Page 1
